channel.title: Peaches or book?
channel.description:
I have enough Mage Training Arena for one of the two.
I can either get bones to peaches (which rocks for long trips)
Or I can get the Mage's book for and sell it for 4.8m.
I will have left over points from the bones to peaches

item.title: Peaches or book?
item.dc:creator: @the_elve_age the elve age
item.description:
@the_elve_age wrote:

Mr Mopar X:

It would be more beneficial to not only use the tabs for monster hunting but profit by making the tabs in your POH. Besides, if you go to avainsie’s they pull in about 400K an hour. A day or two there and you make 4.8M, however, mage book takes like a week at the MTA.

It takes 2 days + mage exp.
